value: Breeds on St. Ambrose Island off the coast of Chile and on the coast of Buenos Aires Province, Argentina. Occurs also on the Chilean coast from Arica to Valdivia and on the east coast of South America from Rio de Janeiro to the Straits of Magellan.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Lagoons and marshes of se Brazil and Uruguay to Patagonia
